headline: Robinhood earnings, Fed comments, retail sales: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime Host Josh Lipton previews several of the biggest stories to come tomorrow, Tuesday, February 10, including earnings results from Robinhood Markets (HOOD), Ford (F), and Coca-Cola (KO); commentary from Federal Reserve officials; and the monthly reading on US retail sales. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime.
